<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="imply-vt">imply <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪm'plaɪ/    美 /ɪm'plaɪ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>含有…的意思；暗示；暗指：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Are you implying that I'm lying?
你是暗指我在撒谎吗？</p></div>

<h4 id="2-suggest">2.<strong>说明；表明 (suggest)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The teacher's smile implied that she had forgiven me.
老师的微笑表明她已经原谅了我。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>implication /ˌɪmplɪ'keɪʃn/ n  [C] &amp; [U]  </p></div>